  <name>Pin It!</name>
  <summary>Pin any apps into the launcher</summary>
  <description>
    <p>
      Add portable apps like raw executable files, AppImage files, etc. into Applications Menu easily. Edit or delete existing desktop files without opening a file manager.
    </p>
    <p>
      Pin It! comes with syntax errors detection, so you will never need to waste your time seeking for why your desktop entry won't be shown in Applications Menu.
    </p>
  </description>
